298
00:26:57,920 --> 00:27:01,315
Daj da vidim. Da vidim.

299
00:27:03,447 --> 00:27:05,447
Ključevi.

300
00:27:08,148 --> 00:27:10,846
G. George Laird.

301
00:27:16,635 --> 00:27:18,635
U redu, bingo.

302
00:27:20,551 --> 00:27:23,944
