00:29:56,707 --> 00:29:59,841
Rekao sam da mi
odmah daš tiket!

325
00:30:12,767 --> 00:30:15,942
Na jebeni pod!
Lezi na jebeni pod!

326
00:30:17,293 --> 00:30:19,293
Jebi se!

